\id 1JN - Kalam NT [kmh] -Papua New Guinea 1992 (DBL 2014) 
\h 1 Jon 
\toc1 Jon Minj Nind Tikak 
\toc2 1 Jon 
\toc3 1 Jon 
\mt1 1 Jon  
\mt2 Jon Minj Nind Tikak  
\imt1 Minim Nind Niŋep  
\ip Bi Jiysis minim dand amemb Jon, minj day nind tikak biy, biynimb Gor apiymiŋay kuyip chiŋgipay gok aŋgrep gen, minim yesek aŋgñimbay ak ma diniŋgiy aŋgiy tikak. Bi Gor minim yesek aŋgep kun gok, minim tuŋgandikiy, biynimb gok kuyip aŋgyiŋgipay, “Mindmaŋgiy key tikjakniŋgamb rek gon, Gor chinup tap bap ma giniŋgamb aŋgiy” monmon giyiŋg, Jiysis biyimb ay owak aŋgiy ma niŋiy, binuk gok kuyip miluk niŋyiŋgipay.  
\ip Kun gey Jon, Jiysis Krays biyimb ay owak ak aŋgñirep gen, niŋrep giy, nup gosimb niŋiy, Gor nup wasemb ay, penpen wasemb ayep ak niŋrep giniŋgiy aŋgiy, minj kun biy tikak.  
\iot Minim Ar Keykey Mindip Rek:  
\io1 Minim nind aŋgak ak mindip, chapta 1:1-4.  
\io1 Gor kind ak sek, kisyim kind ak sek minim ak mindip, chapta 1:5–2:29.  
\io1 Gor Ñapan nuk gok sek, Seytan ñapan nuk gok sek minim ak mindip, chapta 3:1-24.  
\io1 Gor Kawnan tep nuk ak kuyip gos ñek aspay akaŋ, Seytan kichekiy malñiluk tap gok gos ñek aspay akaŋ aŋgiy, niŋrep giy nep, minim kuyip ak dinimimb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 4:1-6.  
\io1 Wasemb ayep miñ ar ak mindip, chapta 4:7-21.  
\io1 Biynimb Jiysis nup Gor Ñinuk yimb aŋgiy, nup gosimb niŋbay gok minim ak mindip, chapta 5:1-21.  
\c 1  
\s1 Minim Maŋgiy Won Permindep Ak  
\p
\v 1 Miñmon alwol gayak ñin ak, Minim Maŋgiy Won ak Nop yip mindek. Pen nuk kisen ñin biy nep apek, windin chin key niŋiy, minim aŋgek timund chinup ak sikek, ñin maŋgiy chin key ak nup diniŋnuk.  
\v 2 Bi gek per mindeniŋgambay kun ak, Nop yip mindiy, chinup per mindeyaŋ aŋgiy apek, miseŋ niŋiy mey, nimbip aspun.  
\v 3 Nup windin niŋiy, minim nup ak niŋiy diy mey, kiy apiymiŋay yip jimñiy mindpun. Pen nimbip minim kun ak aŋgon niŋiy dem mey, chin maŋgiysek Gor apiymiŋay yip jimñiy mindiy, kiñiŋ nokom mindoniŋgambun.  
\v 4 Kun gem mey, tep yimb giniŋgamb aŋgiy, minj biy tiksipun.   
\s1 Melik Ar Ak Taŋgonjun  
\p
\v 5 Krays chinup aŋgek niŋnuk minim ak, nimbip aŋgñiniŋg gispiyn. Gor melik yimb mindip; kisyim sek ma mindip.  
\v 6 Kun ak chin tap siy tap timey gi mindyiŋg, Gor yip jimñiy mindpun aŋgniŋgambun ak; minim nuk niŋind yimb ak kirgiy, kisyimnamb okok mindiy, yesek ar ak gi dand amyiŋg, kun aŋgniŋgambun.  
\v 7 Pen Gor yip mindiy, melik nup ar ak taŋgiy jimñiy mindon, Ñinuk chinup aŋgiy likañ yapek kumak rek, gach chinup wiykyokyiŋg nep mindeniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 8 Pen tap siy tap timey gunap ma gipun aŋgniŋgambun ak; gos nep niŋiy, Gor minim ak ma diy kun aŋgniŋgambun.  
\v 9 Pen tap siy tap timey gipun gok, Gor nup aŋgyikoniŋgambun; nuk Bi suŋ-tep mindip rek, chinup niŋiy kirginiŋgayn aŋgak rek giniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 10 Pen tap siy tap timey ma nep gipun aŋgniŋgambun ak, Gor minim nuk yesek aŋgip aŋgiy, minim nup ak ma diy mey, kun aŋgniŋgambun.   
\c 2  
\s1 Krays Chinup Simb Niŋiy Nop Nup Aŋgniŋ Mindip  
\p
\v 1 Ñapan yand gok. Nimbip minj tiksipiyn ak, tap siy tap timey ma ginimimb aspiyn. Pen tap siy tap timey geniŋgambim, Jiysis Krays chinup simb niŋiy, Nop nup aŋgniŋyiŋg nep mindip rek, tap siy tap timey gipay ak, niŋiy kirginimin aŋgniŋgamb.  
\v 2 Ñinuk tap siy tap timey key ma giy, chinup aŋgiy kumek mey, Nop tap siy tap timey gipun ak, niŋiy kirginiŋgamb. Chinup nep mer, biynimb okok maŋgiysek tap siy tap timey gipay ak, niŋiy kirginimuŋ rek mindip.   
\p
\v 3 Chin Gor aŋgip rek gi mindiy mey; nup gosimb niŋbun ak, niŋrep gipun.  
\v 4 Biynimb gunap Gor biynimb nuk mindpun aŋgiy pen; aŋgip rek ma giniŋgambay ak, yesek yimb aŋgniŋgambay. Minim aŋgniŋgambay kun ak, Bi minim niŋind nep aŋgip ak yip mindiy, ma aŋgniŋgambay.  
\v 5-6 Biynimb Gor aŋgip rek gipay gok, Gor nup gosimb niŋbay. Pen biynimb nup gosimb ma niŋbay gok, biynimb nuk ma mindpay. Krays ker mindpay biynimb gok, nuk gip rek nep giniŋgiy. Nuk gip rek giy mey; nuk yip jimñiy mindpun aŋgiy niŋrep gipun.   
\s1 Penpen Wasemb Aynimimb  
\p
\v 7-8 Buŋgiy yand Krays ker mindpim gok. Minim aŋgniŋg gispiyn ak niŋem, minim kisenimb rek ayniŋgamb ak pen; minim nindnimb wosrey dipik ak nimbip aspiyn. Minim kun ak mey; penpen wasemb aynimimb. Krays biynimb gok kuyip wasemb ayip rek, nimb niŋiy kunep gipim ak niŋbun. Wasemb aynimimb minim kun ak, minim niŋind yimb; chinup sup rek ak puŋgyomimb.   
\p
\v 9 Biynimb mam ay gunap kuyip miluk niŋyiŋg, Gor melik nup diy, biynimb nuk yimb mindpun aŋgniŋgambay ak; minim nep aŋgniŋgambay. Biynimb kun gok rek, kisyimnamb ak nep mindpay.   
\p
\v 10 Biynimb mam ay gok kuyip wasemb aypay gok, Gor melik tep ar ak mindpay. Biynimb gunap kuyip monmon gey, ma apyap pikniŋgambay.  
\v 11 Pen biynimb mam ay gok kuyip miluk niŋniŋgambay gok, kisyim kind ak mindiy, piŋiy aran apyan giyiŋg, amjipun miŋgan ak aŋgiy, ma niŋbay.   
\p
\v 12 Ñapan yand gok. Krays yimb tep mindip rek, Nop nimbip tap siy tap timey gipim ak niŋiy kirgek mey, nimbip minj tiksipiyn.   
\p
\v 13 Nimb biyomb gok; Bi nind kiñiŋ giy mindek ak nup niŋbim rek, nimbip minj tiksipiyn.  
\p Nimb bi paranj gok; Gor minim ak diy, bi timey ak yip penpen gi wiyniym giy mindpim rek, nimbip minj tiksipiyn.  
\p Nimb ñapan gok; Bapiy Gor nup niŋbim ak mey, nimbip minj tiksipiyn.   
\p
\v 14 Nimb biyomb gok; Krays bi nind yimb mindek ak nup niŋbim ak mey, nimbip minj tiksipiyn.  
\p Nimb bi paranj gok; Gor minim ak diy, Seytan nup kirgiy mindrep gipim ak mey, nimbip minj tiksipiyn.   
\s1 Tap Mankumb Biy Ker Gok Mindmaŋgiy Ma Aynimimb  
\p
\v 15 Gor ker ma mindpay gok, miñ gipay ar ak ginjun aŋgiy, ma niŋnimimb. Gos nimbip tap lum ar biy am kom kom gek, Gor nup gos ak kirginiŋgambim.  
\v 16 Biynimb tap lum ar biy gosimb niŋbay gok, windin niŋiy gos timey wip rek giy, mindmaŋgiy key limgip rek giy, yimb yomb dinjun aŋgiy niŋbay rek gey amimb. Gor kuyip gos ñek kun ma gipay; nup ma chiŋgipay rek, gos kun ak niŋiy ar kun ak ambay.  
\v 17 Tap gos lip gip kun gok, pisnep kurginiŋg gisap ak pen; biynimb Gor giyaŋ aŋgiy niŋimb rek gipay gok, perper mindeniŋgambay.   
\s1 Ñin Kisen Ak Maŋ Mindip  
\p
\v 18 Ñapan yand gok. Ñin kisen ak maŋ mindip. Bi Krays nup miluk niŋep ak, biyomb rek ayek nup niŋniŋgambay aŋgyak ak niŋbim. Miñiy biynimb Krays nup miluk niŋbay gok kuŋay mindpay ak mey, ñin kisen ak, maŋ mindip ak niŋbun.   
\p
\v 19 Biynimb Krays nup miluk niŋbay kun gok, biynimb chin yimb mindembiyap rek, chinup kirgiy keykey ma ambiyap. Kun giy kiriŋg keykey amniyak rek, biynimb chin yimb ma mindpay ak, miseŋ yimb niŋbun.   
\p
\v 20 Pen Krays, Gor Kawnan yokek ap nimb yip mindakniŋ, minim yipul yimb ak niŋiy dipim.  
\v 21 Niŋnimimb aŋgiy minj biy ma tiksipiyn; niŋbim rek nimbip tiksipiyn. Gor minim yipul niŋind yimb nuk ak, minim yesek gok yip ma wopsakip ak kunep niŋbim.   
\p
\v 22 Biynimb an rek minim yesek apay? Mey biynimb Jiysis nup Biyomb Krays mer, bi yikop bap aŋgiy, nup miluk niŋbay gok. Nop yip, Ñinuk yip kuyip kirgiy mey, kun ak rek apay.  
\v 23 Ñinuk nup kirpay gok, Nop nup kunep kirpay. Pen biynimb Ñinuk nup dipay gok, Nop nup sek dipay.   
\s1 Gor Kawnan Ak Chinup Minim Niŋind Ak Aŋgñimb  
\p
\v 24 Kun ak minim nind niŋbik ak, direp giyiŋg mindiy mey, Gor apiymiŋay yip jimñiy mindeniŋgambim.  
\v 25 Kiy apiymiŋay yip jimñiy mindiy mey, Krays biynimb nuk dip gok perper mindeniŋgambay aŋgak rek, nimbip giniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 26 Biynimb nimbip tom gispay kun gok, tom gi dand amey, apyap piknimimb rek ayek niŋiy, nimbip minj biy tiksipiyn.  
\v 27 Pen minim kuŋay ma aŋgniŋgayn. Gor Kawnan yip mindpim ak mey, nuk key nimbip gos yipund giy ar ak ñek, niŋrep giniŋgambim. Minim yesek ar gok, gos ñek ma niŋniŋgambun; yipund giniŋgamb ar ak nep, gos ñek niŋniŋgambun. Kun ak Gor Kawnan gos ñimb rek, Krays nup chiŋgiy nep mindenimimb.   
\p
\v 28 Ñapan yand gok. Krays nup chiŋgiy nep mindem mey, nuk andkind winiŋgamb ñin ak, nup niŋon nambiŋ ma giniŋgamb; wisimb yapiy nep mindeniŋgambun.  
\v 29 Chin niŋbun: Gor Ñinuk Krays suŋ-tep mindiy, miñ yipund gip ar ak nep gip. Kun ak biynimb miñ yipund gip ar ak gipay gok, Gor ñapan nuk mindiy mey, kun gipay.   
\c 3  
\s1 Gor Ñapan Nuk Mindpun Ak Niŋiy Mindrep Ginjun  
\p
\v 1 Gor chinup wasemb yimb ay ñapan yand aŋgip ak, wal apiyn. Pen biynimb yikop gok, niŋind chinup ma dipay. Bapiy chin ak nup diy rek, chinup dipyap.  
\v 2 Pen buŋgiy tep yand gok niŋim! Miñiy Gor ñapan nuk mindpun ak, kisen key yimb mindoniŋgambun. Yerip rek mindoniŋgambun ak, niŋrep ma gipun ak pen, nuk miseŋ gek nup niŋiy, chin biynimb kun gok key yimb ay, nuk mindip rek ak mindoniŋgambun.  
\v 3 Biynimb gos tep kun ak niŋbay gok, Krays suŋ-tep mindip rek mindenjun aŋgiy, mindrep yimb gipay.   
\p
\v 4 Biynimb tap siy tap timey gipay gok, Gor nup minim ak timbrikpay. Tap siy tap timey ak key mer; mey minim nup timbrikpun ak nep.  
\v 5 Pen chin niŋbun: Jiysis tap siy tap timey gipay rek niŋiy awak. Nuk tap siy tap timey ma gip ak mey;  
\v 6 biynimb nuk gek kim kisenimb rek mindpay gok, tap siy tap timey giyiŋg ma mindeniŋgambay. Biynimb tap siy tap timey gi mindpay gok, nuk bi yerip rek mindip ak ma niŋiy, nup ma chiŋgipay.   
\p
\v 7 Ñapan tep yand gok. Biynimb gunap nimbip nembnemb gi dand kind kiyk okok amniŋgiy rek ayip ak, niŋrep ginimimb. Biynimb mindrep gipay gok, Krays suŋ-tep mindip rek mindpay.  
\v 8 Pen biynimb tap siy tap timey giyiŋg mindpay gok, Seytan bak ayek, nuk tap siy tap timey per gip rek gi mindpay. Ar kun ak nep, Gor Ñinuk apiy, Seytan biynimb gok kuyip timey giyiŋgip miñ ak, timbrikak.  
\v 9 Biynimb Gor ñapan nuk mindpay gok, nuk mindrep gip rek mindiy, tap siy tap timey gok asikrep gipay. Nuk mindip rek mindiy, tap siy tap timey gi mindeniŋgiy rek ma ayip.  
\v 10 Kun ak Gor ker mindpay akaŋ, Seytan ker mindpay ak niŋrep gipun. Biynimb mindrep ma giy, mam ay gok kuyip wasemb ma aypay gok; Gor ñapan nuk ma mindpay.   
\s1 Mam Ay Gor Ker Mindpay Gok Kuyip Wasemb Aynimimb  
\p
\v 11 Pen nimbip kiñiŋ giy aŋgiy per apun rek: mam ay gok kuyip wasemb aynimimb.  
\v 12 Andam ñinuk Keyn gak rek ma ginjun. Nuk Seytan ker mindiy, numam kisen mindrep gak ak nup, miluk niŋiy, pisnep pikayek kumak.  
\v 13 Kun ak mam ay yand gok. Biynimb yikop gok nimbip niŋey miluk yowniŋgamb ak, gos kuŋay ma niŋnimimb. Ak yikop kun giniŋgambay.   
\p
\v 14 Chin mam ay gok kuyip wasemb aypun rek niŋbun: Gor chinup dek, pisnep kumbay kind ak kirgiy, perper mindeniŋgambay kind ak opun. Biynimb wasemb ma aypay gok, pisnep kumbay kind ak mindnep mindpay.  
\v 15 Biynimb mam ay gunap kuyip miluk niŋbay gok, biynimb chip ñapay gok rek ayip. Pen biynimb chip ñapay gok, yergiy perper mindeniŋgambay.   
\p
\v 16 Krays chinup simb niŋiy kumak rek, chin mam ay gunap kuyip simb niŋiy, monmon direp ginjun.  
\v 17 Biynimb tap kuŋay mindakniŋ, mam ay tap tikdip gok kuyip, simb ma niŋniŋgambay gok, yergiy Bapiy Gor biynimb simb niŋimb rek, gipun aŋgniŋgambay.  
\v 18 Kun ak ñapan yand gok. Minim nep ma aŋgjun, mam ay gok kuyip wasemb yimb ayjun.   
\s1 Biynimb Gor Nup Chiŋgipay Gok Wisimb Yapiy Nep Mindpay  
\p
\v 19 Kuyip wasemb yimb ay mey, minim yipul yimb direp gipun ak, niŋrep giniŋgambun. Gor windin yirik ar ak chin nambiŋ ma diy, wisimb yapiy nep mindoniŋgambun.  
\v 20 Chin key gos par ayiŋg mindoniŋgambun ak; Gor Biyomb yimb gos timund chinup maŋgiysek niŋrep gip ak niŋek, tep ma yimb giniŋgamb.  
\v 21 Kun ak biynimb yand gok niŋim: aŋgip rek giy mey, gos kuŋay ma niŋiy, Gor windin yirik ar ak ñawil ma diniŋgambun.  
\v 22 Minim aŋgip rek giyiŋg nup aŋgniŋoniŋgambun, tep gakniŋ, aŋgniŋgambun rek giniŋgamb.  
\v 23 Pen chinup aŋgak rek giniŋg, Ñinuk Jiysis Krays nup gosimb niŋiy, mam ay gok kuyip wasemb ayjun.  
\v 24 Biynimb aŋgip rek gipay gok, nuk kiy yip mindek; kiy pen nuk yip mindpay. Kawnan nuk yokek ap chin yip mindpun ak, nuk yip jimñiy mindpun ak niŋbun.   
\c 4  
\s1 Gor Kawnan Tep Ak Akaŋ, Tap Key Bap Kuyip Gos Ñimb  
\p
\v 1 Buŋgiy tep yand gok. Biynimb Gor minim yesek aŋgrapay gok kuŋay mindpay ak mey, biynimb gunap Gor Kawnan yip mindpun aŋgeniŋgiy niŋrep giy minim kuyip ak dinimimb. Gor Kawnan apay ak pen: Gor Kawnan yipund giy akaŋ, tap gunap key kuyip gos ñek aspay akaŋ aŋgiy niŋnimimb.  
\v 2 Pen Gor Kawnan ak yip mindiy aŋgniŋgambay, “Bi Jiysis Krays ak, Gor Ñinuk. Nuk biyimb ay owak aŋgniŋgambay.”  
\v 3 Pen Gor Ñinuk biyimb rek ay ma awak aŋgniŋgambay ak; Gor Kawnan ak yip ma mindeniŋgambay. Tap Krays nup miluk niŋimb bap yip mindiy mey, minim kun ak rek aŋgniŋgambay. Biynimb kun ak rek mindeniŋgambay aŋgey niŋbik. Pen miñiy gunap mindpay ak; niŋrep ginimimb.   
\p
\v 4 Ñapan yand gok. Nimb Gor biynimb nuk mindpim rek, minim yesek kiyk apay ak, taw achip achip gipim. Kawnan niŋind yimb nimbip gos ñimb ak, kilis timey yimb; kuyip gos ñimb ak, kilis ma mindip.  
\v 5 Kiyk biynimb yikop tap lum biy nimb gok gosimb niŋbay ak mey; tap yikop lum ar biy nimb minim ak aŋgey niŋbay.  
\v 6 Pen chin Gor Ñapan nuk mindpun rek, biynimb Gor nup dipay gok, minim chinup ak dipay. Biynimb nup ma dipay gok, minim chinup ak ma dipay. Ar kun ak Gor Kawnan yip mindiy apay akaŋ, tap bap key gos ñek apay ak niŋbun.   
\s1 Gor Chinup Wasemb Yimb Ayip  
\p
\v 7 Biynimb tep yand gok. Gor biynimb nuk mindpun ak, penpen wasemb ayjun. Biynimb wasemb aypay gok, Gor nup chiŋgiy, ñapan nuk mindiy mey, wasemb aypay.  
\v 8 Pen biynimb wasemb ma aypay gok, Gor bi biynimb wasemb ayip ak nup ma dipay.  
\v 9 Chinup wasemb yimb ayip rek niŋyaŋ aŋgiy, Ñinuk nokom yimb ak yokek apiy gek, perper mindonjun rek ayip.  
\v 10 Wasemb yimb ayep ar ak, chinup kind ak ma tikjakak; Gor kind nuk ak tikjakak. Chinup wasemb ay Ñinuk nup yokek apiy, tap siy tap timey gipun rek simboŋgak.   
\p
\v 11 Buŋgiy tep yand gok. Nuk chinup kun giy wasemb yimb ayip ak; chin ñapan nuk gok, penpen wasemb ayjun.  
\v 12 Gor nup miseŋ ma niŋbun ak pen; penpen wasemb aypun ak keynep ma gipun, nuk chin yip mindakniŋ gipun. Nuk chin yip mindip ak mey, nuk biynimb wasemb yimb ayip rek gipun.  
\v 13 Chinup Kawnan nuk yokek yip mindiy mey, nuk yip nep mindpun ak niŋrep gipun.  
\v 14 Nop Ñinuk bi biynimb di jimñemb ak yokek apek, windin chin key niŋnuk ak mey; biynimb miñmon okok keykey kuyip gos niŋiy yokak ak, niŋrep giy biynimb aŋgñimbun.  
\v 15 Biynimb Jiysis Gor Ñinuk yimb aŋgiy miseŋ apay gok, Gor kiy yip mindakniŋ, nup chiŋgiy, kun ak rek niŋiy apay.  
\v 16 Chin key Gor wasemb ayip ak niŋrep giy, ar kun ak gon amimb.  
\p Gor bi wasemb ayep. Biynimb wasemb aypay gok, nup chiŋgey kiy yip mindakniŋ, wasemb aypay.  
\v 17 Chin Gor nup gosimb niŋbun gok, Krays mindip rek mindiy, biynimb gunap kuyip direp yimb gipun. Kun ak kor yomb giniŋgamb ak niŋon, jel ma gip.  
\v 18 Biynimb penpen wasemb yimb aypay gok, penpen niŋey, jel ma giniŋgamb. Kun ak rek, chin biynimb Gor yip penpen wasemb yimb aypun gok, kunep jel gek ma pirikpun. Biynimb pirikpay gok, Gor nup wasemb yimb ma aypay.   
\p
\v 19 Gor nuk key chinup wasemb ayek mey, nup pen wasemb aypun.  
\v 20 Biynimb Gor nup wasemb aypun aŋgniŋgambay ak pen; mam ay gok kuyip miluk niŋniŋgambay ak, yesek nep aŋgniŋgambay. Biynimb miseŋ niŋbay gok kuyip, miluk niŋniŋgambay ak, yergiy Gor bi miseŋ ma niŋbay ak nup, wasemb ayniŋgambay.  
\v 21 Gor aŋgak, “Biynimb yip wasemb ayniŋgiy gok, mam ay gok kuyip kunep wasemb ayniŋgiy aŋgak.”   
\c 5  
\s1 Biynimb Jiysis Nup Dipay Gok  
\p
\v 1 Biynimb Jiysis bi Kiyŋ yomb key yimb kond mindyiŋgipun ak nep wip aŋgiy niŋbay gok; Gor ñapan nuk mindiy, nup wasemb ay, Ñinuk nup wasemb ay gipay.  
\v 2 Pen biynimb Gor nup wasemb ayniŋgambay gok, aŋgip rek giyiŋg, ñapan nuk gunap kuyip wasemb ayniŋgambay.   
\p
\v 3 Gor nup wasemb ay mey, aŋgip rek giniŋgambun. Minim nuk aŋgip kun ak, miker ma gip.  
\v 4 Nup gosimb niŋon, chinup dek ñapan nuk mindpun ak, biynimb yikop gok miñ gipay ar ak, gos chinup lipiŋg dand amnimuŋ rek ma ayniŋgamb. Nup gosimb niŋmindon, chinup kond mindek mindrep giniŋgambun.  
\v 5 Chin biynimb Jiysis Gor Ñinuk yimb aŋgiy niŋbun gok, miñ giy yiwur dipay kun ak kirginiŋgambun; pen biynimb nup gosimb ma niŋbay gok, kirginiŋgiy rek ma ayniŋgamb.   
\s1 Jiysis Gor Ñinuk Yimb  
\p
\v 6 Jiysis owak ak bi yikop ma owak. Ñiŋg pikñeyak, kisen likañ yapek kumak. Ñiŋg nep pikek, Gor Ñinuk ak aŋgiy ma apun; ñiŋg pikek kisen likañ yapiy kumak ak, Gor Ñinuk mindip ak niŋbun. Gor Kawnan nuk ak kunep chinup gos ñek niŋbun: Jiysis Gor Ñinuk yimb ak mindip.  
\v 7 Kun ak minim ar omiŋal nokom mindip:   
\q1
\v 8 Jiysis nup ñiŋg pikyak ak, likañ nuk yowak ak,  
\q1 Nop Kawnan ak Ñiyand aŋgiy, chinup gos ñimb ak.  
\m Minim omiŋal nokom kun ak, jimñiy ar nokom aŋgip rek, Jiysis Gor Ñinuk nep mindip ak niŋrep gipun.  
\v 9 Biynimb gok aŋgey niŋbun ak, minim nep aŋgey niŋbun; Gor Ñinuk chinup minim aŋgip ak, niŋind yimb aŋgip.   
\p
\v 10 Biynimb Jiysis Gor Ñinuk yimb aŋgiy niŋbay gok, Gor yip mindiy, kun giy niŋbay. Pen biynimb Jiysis Gor Ñinuk mer aŋgiy niŋbay gok, Gor bi yesek aŋgip aŋgiy kun giy niŋbay.  
\v 11 Nuk Ñiyand ak yoken am gek, perper mindeniŋgiy aŋgak rek,  
\v 12 Ñinuk nup dipay biynimb gok, perper mindeniŋgambay; pen nup ma dipay gok, perper mindeniŋgiy rek ma ayip.   
\s1 Gor Nup Dipim Rek Ñapan Nuk Mindpim  
\p
\v 13 Nimb Gor Ñinuk chinup di Nop yip jimñimb aŋgiy, nup gosimb niŋbim gok, perper mindeniŋgambim ak niŋrep ginimimb aŋgiy, minj kun biy tiksipiyn.   
\p
\v 14-15 Gor nup tep giniŋgamb ar gok aŋgniŋoniŋgambun, aŋgniŋniŋgambun rek nep giniŋgamb ak, niŋrep gipun.   
\p
\v 16 Pen mam ay bap tap siy tap timey gey niŋiy, Gor nup aŋgniŋnimimb. Aŋgniŋem, kuyip tip ak dek, nuk yip jimñiy mindeniŋgambay. Pen tap siy tap timey mon key yinjap amemb rek ak geniŋgiy, Gor nup aŋgniŋnimimb aŋgiy ma asipiyn.  
\v 17 Gor tap mer aŋgip gok gipay ak, tap siy tap timey gipay ak pen; tap timey ar gunap gey, Gor niŋiy kirginimuŋ rek ayniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 18 Chin niŋbun: biynimb Gor ñapan nuk mindpay gok, tap siy tap timey giyiŋg ma mindpay; Gor Ñinuk kuyip kond mindek, Seytan kuyip dinimuŋ rek ma ayip.   
\p
\v 19 Chin niŋbun: biynimb yikop gok maŋgiysek Seytan ker mindpay; chin pen Gor ker mindpun.   
\p
\v 20 Gor Ñinuk awak rek, Gor yipund giy ak nup niŋrep gipun. Amemb owep chinup ak, Gor yipund giy ak kond mindip. Gor yipund giy kun ak mey, Jiysis Krays. Nuk gak ak perper mindeniŋgambun.   
\p
\v 21 Ñapan yand gok. Gor chin aŋgiy tap yesek aŋgniŋbay gok, asikrep ginimimb.   